&gt;
&gt;   From other hand we don&#39;t really have to cover parse method in your 
&gt;example because exceptional case most likely will affect the caller 
&gt;code and that is where erroroous outcome will caise most of the 
&gt;troubles. Though it can be easily reproduced with mocks... but of 
&gt;course not for static methods. :-)
&gt;
&gt;   Using DFA (like it is done in Agitator) allows to have sort of 
